{"task_id": "TASK-022", "timestamp": "2026-01-06T12:00:00Z", "finding_type": "feature", "source_url": "https://signaturerail.com/", "content": "Signature Rail is a specialist railway software provider trusted by complex railways worldwide. Originated in UK with 30+ years experience. Parent company is Modaxo (Constellation Software).", "relevance": "high"}
{"task_id": "TASK-022", "timestamp": "2026-01-06T12:01:00Z", "finding_type": "feature", "source_url": "https://signaturerail.com/planning-solutions/", "content": "TrainPlan (flagship product since 1994): Creates train schedules and provides planners with tools to manage timetabling across all time horizons (long-term, short-term, very short-term planning), including changes required for possessions and unexpected events.", "relevance": "high"}
{"task_id": "TASK-022", "timestamp": "2026-01-06T12:02:00Z", "finding_type": "feature", "source_url": "https://signaturerail.com/planning-solutions/", "content": "Core capabilities: Automatic conflict validation, 'what if' scenario planning, extensive calendaring functionality, resource allocation and constraint management, variant vehicle diagrams for special events.", "relevance": "high"}
{"task_id": "TASK-022", "timestamp": "2026-01-06T12:03:00Z", "finding_type": "ui", "source_url": "https://signaturerail.com/planning-solutions/", "content": "Interface approach: Powerful graphic and tabular displays with complete display of service schedule information. Visual clarity on graphs for accurate results. Supports bulk modification and addition of services.", "relevance": "high"}
{"task_id": "TASK-022", "timestamp": "2026-01-06T12:04:00Z", "finding_type": "ui", "source_url": "https://signaturerail.com/2021/10/18/demonstrating-trainplan-video-collection/", "content": "TrainPlan interface offers visual and tabular displays - multiple views of service schedule information for easier modification. Uses train graphs (time-distance diagrams) similar to Marey charts.", "relevance": "high"}
{"task_id": "TASK-022", "timestamp": "2026-01-06T12:05:00Z", "finding_type": "feature", "source_url": "https://signaturerail.com/on-the-day-solutions/", "content": "On-the-Day Operations: Visual dashboards for real-time train reassignment during disruptions (landslip, flood, breakdown, weather). Uses optimised process considering maintenance status and driver locations.", "relevance": "high"}
{"task_id": "TASK-022", "timestamp": "2026-01-06T12:06:00Z", "finding_type": "feature", "source_url": "https://signaturerail.com/on-the-day-solutions/", "content": "Disruption management: Tracks fuel distances, maintenance distances, crew hours and costs. Contingency layers can be pre-saved. Real-time de-assign and re-assign of trains.", "relevance": "high"}
{"task_id": "TASK-022", "timestamp": "2026-01-06T12:07:00Z", "finding_type": "feature", "source_url": "https://modaxo.com/our-brands/signature-rail/", "content": "Enterprise Rail Suite includes: TrainPlan (timetabling), RailPlan (signalling design support), Power Modelling, Rostering, On-the-Day management of Stock and Crew.", "relevance": "high"}
{"task_id": "TASK-022", "timestamp": "2026-01-06T12:08:00Z", "finding_type": "feature", "source_url": "https://signaturerail.com/providing-the-rail-planning-system-to-succeed/", "content": "Customer testimonial: 'It used to take my team around 10 minutes to identify conflicts which would often be the root cause of disruption - with TrainPlan it takes 10 seconds.'", "relevance": "medium"}
{"task_id": "TASK-022", "timestamp": "2026-01-06T12:09:00Z", "finding_type": "tech", "source_url": "https://signaturerail.com/", "content": "Website built on WordPress/Elementor. No public information about internal software technology stack. Software described as 'software-for-life' implying long-term enterprise stability.", "relevance": "low"}
{"task_id": "TASK-022", "timestamp": "2026-01-06T12:10:00Z", "finding_type": "feature", "source_url": "https://signaturerail.com/2021/10/18/demonstrating-trainplan-video-collection/", "content": "TrainPlan demos cover: 1) Creating variant vehicle diagrams for special events, 2) Managing over-running engineering works, 3) Assigning uncovered train services, 4) Planning/tracking fuelling activities (including BI-mode fleets).", "relevance": "high"}
{"task_id": "TASK-022", "timestamp": "2026-01-06T12:11:00Z", "finding_type": "ui", "source_url": "https://www.researchgate.net/figure/Travel-graph-used-for-visualising-the-train-timetables_fig1_317421644", "content": "Railway industry standard visualization: Train graphs (Marey charts) with horizontal axis for time, vertical axis for stops/stations. Slope indicates relative speed. First used 1840s by Charles Ibry.", "relevance": "medium"}
{"task_id": "TASK-022", "timestamp": "2026-01-06T12:12:00Z", "finding_type": "feature", "source_url": "https://signaturerail.com/resources/", "content": "Metrolinx case study: Signature Rail supports 'the largest transportation investment in Ontario's history'. Global presence: Norway, Sweden, UK, Australia, USA, Canada.", "relevance": "medium"}
{"task_id": "TASK-022", "timestamp": "2026-01-06T12:13:00Z", "finding_type": "feature", "source_url": "https://signaturerail.com/planning-solutions/", "content": "Key differentiator: All data accessible in one user-friendly system enabling lightning fast production, validation and communication of plans. Customized implementations for specific operator requirements.", "relevance": "high"}
{"task_id": "TASK-022", "timestamp": "2026-01-06T12:14:00Z", "finding_type": "ui", "source_url": "https://signaturerail.com/on-the-day-solutions/", "content": "Dashboard design philosophy: Controllers have high degree of confidence in actions and decisions. Downstream systems receive trusted information. Focus on situational awareness during disruption.", "relevance": "high"}

